publicwhip.spmotion: *S3M-7183 Cathy Jamieson: 10 Years of yipworld.com—That the Parliament congratulates yipworld.com, based in Cumnock, on its 10th anniversary; considers that Janice Hendry and her dedicated team of staff and volunteers have carried out innovative work; recognises the contribution made by yipworld.com’s board of directors and East Ayrshire Council; notes that yipworld.com has been successful in securing funding to run a men into childcare course, and wishes the project every success in its future work with young people.
